loosing weight after a c section i had a c section weeks ago i already lost pounds doing nothing but breastfeeding but have more pounds to go until my pre pregnancy weight of since i just had her there isnt much exercise i can do until i am completely healed what did other moms do in thie situation i want to tighten up my tummy you've already lost a bunch of weight congrats i do have to warn you though about trying to do stuff too fast i thought that i was invincible after my second c section i was taking it easy not lifting my oldest child too much etc i was doing everything correctly anyway i sat on the floor one day with my kids at a family party and when i got up i felt my incision rip open i was already almost completely healed i think about weeks after i had my son but after that incident it took another weeks to heal my point is just relax and enjoy your baby you'll have plenty of time to work off the tummy after you're healed Breastfeeding Pregnancy Care Bears Urinary incontinence Childbirth Bubble Bobble Dieting The Contender (television series) Breech birth Fertility awareness Time Out of Mind Muscle Caesarean section Charmed Abortion debate Adjustable gastric band Weight training Stuttering Sailing USS Wasp (CV-18) Sauna Nipple piercing Social rule Mattress Birth weight Brassiere Stress fracture Super Size Me Obstetrics The Amazing Race Textile manufacturing Fecal incontinence Treehouse of Horror V Baby Blues Tocopherol Planet Waves The Family from One End Street Aerial (dance move) Premature birth Infantilism Cliff Richard USS Yorktown (CV-10) Massage About a Boy The Price Is Right Race and intelligence (Culture-only or partially-genetic explanation) Ben Johnson (athlete) Doug Disney's Adventures of the Gummi Bears Babe Carey Chair Neighbours Hey Jude Glossary of climbing terms Coeliac disease Elevator Laura Schlessinger Kain (Legacy of Kain) Force The Brady Bunch Jeopardy! Professional wrestling holds Anorexia nervosa Spina bifida EastEnders Fire Emblem